      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Peter Gillgasch</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:194px;\"><a href=\"/File:PeterGillgasch.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/8/84/PeterGillgasch.jpg\" width=\"192\" height=\"215\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:PeterGillgasch.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Peter Gillgasch <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Peter W. Gillgasch</b>,<br />\na German computer scientist, software developer and former computer chess programmer. In 1992, while undergraduate at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karlsruhe_Institute_of_Technology\">University of Karlsruhe</a> he developed the <a href=\"/Pascal\" title=\"Pascal\">Pascal</a> predecessor of a computer chess program which later evolved to <a href=\"/DarkThought\" title=\"DarkThought\">DarkThought</a> after he joined forces with <a href=\"/Ernst_A._Heinz\" title=\"Ernst A. Heinz\">Ernst A. Heinz</a> in 1993 and later in 1994 with <a href=\"/Markus_Gille\" title=\"Markus Gille\">Markus Gille</a>. Gillgasch created <a href=\"/Rotated_Bitboards\" title=\"Rotated Bitboards\">rotated bitboards</a> with a different diagonal mapping than <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt</a>, later described by Heinz <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> . He left the DarkThought team in April 1996 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> . \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1995_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1995 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Gillgasch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1995_...\">1995 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Gillgasch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1995 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/eHsFoX1Msi0/v5p_K9RjdXoJ\">Re: World Championship of Computers</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Gillgasch</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, July 04, 1995&#160;» <a href=\"/WCCC_1995\" title=\"WCCC 1995\">WCCC 1995</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/msg/3586cb164110dd2e\">Re: Quiescence search problems</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Gillgasch</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, August 2, 1995</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/msg/1a47be6e76f9d3f6\">Re: Chess programming using bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Gillgasch</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, August 18, 1995</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/msg/b8bdef757df5d5c9\">Drawn games (Was Re: Transposition table)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Gillgasch</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, February 06, 1996</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://computer-programming-forum.com/47-c-language/e506a63f34a33578.htm\">bit parallelism (WAS: Programming Language Complexity)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Gillgasch</a>, Computer Programming Language Forum - C Language, September 18, 1997</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Gillgasch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=91927\">Re: DB NPS (anyone know the position used)?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter W. Gillgasch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 25, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Deep_Blue\" title=\"Deep Blue\">Deep Blue</a>, <a href=\"/Nodes_per_Second\" title=\"Nodes per Second\">Nodes per Second</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Gillgasch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=188\">Peter Gillgasch's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.xing.com/profile/Peter_Gillgasch\">Peter Gillgasch - Softwareentwickler</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XING\">XING</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Gillgasch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Peter Gillgasch at <a href=\"/WCCC_1995\" title=\"WCCC 1995\">WCCC 1995</a>. Image clipped from <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#18_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 18, No. 3</a>, pp. 178, Photo courtesy by <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://people.csail.mit.edu/heinz/dt/node8.html\">Rotated Bitboards</a> by <a href=\"/Ernst_A._Heinz\" title=\"Ernst A. Heinz\">Ernst A. Heinz</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://people.csail.mit.edu/heinz/dt/node1.html#acknlg\">DarkThought - Acknowledgements</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=473371\">Re: About Deep Blue</a> by <a href=\"/Vincent_Diepeveen\" title=\"Vincent Diepeveen\">Vincent Diepeveen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 23, 2005</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301081128\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 79/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 170/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:3633-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301081128 and revision id 7992\n -->\n"
